        </item>
        <item>
            <title>18 岁自闭黑客涉泄露 GTA 6 片段　被判终身医院令</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/22/gta-6-4/tech-secure/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=gta-6-4</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/22/gta-6-4/tech-secure/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 22 Dec 2023 03:52:32 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[资讯保安]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[GTA 6]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[LAPSUS$]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Rockstar Games]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1211495</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">一位 18 岁英国黑客，早前因泄露了 Rockstar Games 游戏大作 GTA 6 的片段而被捕，最终因严重自闭症及多次出现暴力行为，因而被法院颁布终身医院令。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1211496 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-22-at-11.03.42-AM-694x387.png" alt="" width="694" height="387" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-22-at-11.03.42-AM-694x387.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-22-at-11.03.42-AM-1280x714.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-22-at-11.03.42-AM-768x429.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-22-at-11.03.42-AM-1536x857.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-22-at-11.03.42-AM.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲18 岁黑客 Arion Kurtaj 是国际黑客组织 Lapsus$ 的骨干成员，曾经多次策划并攻击多间知名企业</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">法院聆讯中提及，Arion Kurtaj 在困禁间多次造成伤害或财产损坏。医生诊断为严重自闭症，并不适合受审，加上心理健康评估报告指出，若被告重获自由，就有意图再次犯罪。而陪审团只需要判断 Arion Kurtaj 有否犯罪，而不用考虑其犯罪意图。在保释期间，Arion Kurtaj 亦有继续黑客活动，他使用了 Amazon Firestick、旅馆电视及手机入侵 Rockstar Games。窃取了 90 条未正式发布的游戏影片，以「TeaPotUberHacker」在网上发布影片及源代码。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">18 岁黑客 Arion Kurtaj 是国际黑客组织 Lapsus$ 的骨干成员，曾经多次策划并攻击多间知名企业，包括 Uber、Nvidia 和 Rockstar Games 等等，令受害企业损失超过 1000 万美元（约 7800 万港元）。</p><p>资料及图片来源：<a href="https://www.bbc.com/news/technology-67663128">BBC</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/22/gta-6-4/tech-secure/">18 岁自闭黑客涉泄露 GTA 6 片段　被判终身医院令</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
